'''Sedi Fisk''' lived in a [[Sedi Fisk's desert manor|manor]] in the [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]] desert. He was known by other locals. At some point, Fisk decided to abandon his manor for unknown reasons, without telling anybody. Eventually, it was overrun with [[Womp rat/Legends|womp rats]]. Around [[0 ABY/Legends|0 ABY]], the manor was discovered by a team of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] agents looking for [[Adar Tallon/Legends|Adar Tallon]].<ref name="Tatooine Manhunt">''[[Tatooine Manhunt]]''</ref>

